The one hour course includes a series of interactive tasks.
In one section, the students see the image of a room in a living room and click on coffee bags, curtains, training shoes and books. They receive information on the effects of caffeine and light, as well as the effects of sleeping deficiency on the sporty performance and the importance of a sleep routine.
